test_odd_range:
assert [5, 7] == [121, 121, 121, 121, 121]
  At index 0 diff: 5 != 121
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: 121
  Full diff:
  - [121, 121, 121, 121, 121]
  + [5, 7]
test_all_zero_range:
assert [5, 7] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 5
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [5, 7]
